## Third-party acknowledgements

This project is designed to run [FluidNC](https://github.com/bdring/FluidNC) firmware and the [FluidDial](https://github.com/bdring/FluidDial) pendant firmware, both licensed under GPL v3. Neither project's source code or binaries are distributed here. Users install those firmwares independently.
